data.text:
@marcuswalfrid Hej, meddelandet att du kan boka om skickas till alla som har flyg som kan påverkas av strejken, men det betyder inte att flyget har blivit inställt.

Om flyget ställs in får du ett specifikt meddelade som meddelar det 
//Henrik

@dreamawakehours Hi, if only you should rebook, the booking must be split to two

If it is a group booking, you need to contact the agent the trip is booked with via email

If it is a regular booking with several people, we can help you with chat or phone

@stargirl135 Hi @stargirl135, we have a chat bot here https://t.co/fxd6BsWkM5
To chat with a live agent, choose the category "Chat with Customer Service" and the bot will transfer you when one is available.
Kind regards, Mikael.

@Mr_Kilroy Hi @Mr_Kilroy,
You can send a claim to our customer care department via this link: https://t.co/cXegpq56aG
Kind regards, Mikael.

@XuanZha51931973 Hi! 

We sadly don't know how long the strike will continue, but we are working on resolving it as soon as possible. 

//Kind regards, Dennis

@iamsss123456 Hi! 

We sadly can't guarantee anything in this situation but i would recommend to rebook to a flight that is operated by a subsidiary if possible, as they usually go as planned.
The best i can recommend is to contact our customer service.

//Kind regards, Dennis

@a_t_c86 Hi! 

I'm sorry if you have problems with our site. It's probably a temporary bug so i recommend that you try again a little bit later. 

//Kind regards, Dennis

@Yuan61249157 Hi! 

I apologize that you were affected by the strike. We will notify you as soon as we know if the flight will be cancelled or not, but it's sadly hard to say as it depends on the strike. But we hope to resolve it as soon as possible.

//Kind regards, Dennis

@Yr_Obt_Svt Hi! 

Happy to see that you enjoyed your trip with us. Please call your travel agency so they can help you with your trip if you have any questions.
Please also remove this tweet if possible as it seems your booking reference is in it.

//Kind regards, Dennis

@Yuan61249157 Hi! 

We sadly don't know how long the strike will last. But we are working on solving it as fast as possible. 

//Kind regards, Dennis

@Conrad69192842 Hi! 

I'm sorry if your bag has been delayed. The best i can recommend is to create a report about it at the airport you arrived to, they will then contact you as soon as they get any new information about your bag. 

//Kind regards, Dennis

@alexiaparra Hi! 

All documents need to be valid before you board the flight, so if you try to board before your visa validity starts then you will be denied. So i sadly can't recommend that in this case.

//Kind regards, Dennis

@iamsss123456 Hi! 

Yes if your flight is cancelled then we will be able to change it to a Star Alliance flight depending on if there are any seats left. 

//Kind regards, Dennis

@HudaKhilji Hello! 

You can save the receipts and send us a compensation request after the trip is done so we can help you. 
https://t.co/xMt9zSrqJc

//Kind regards, Dennis

@mr1029 Hi! 

We can sometimes rebook you automatically, but if you don't get any information about it then i recommend that you contact us so we can help you rebook the trip. 

//Kind regards, Dennis

@freskco Hello! 

I'm sorry that your flight was affected. The best i can recommend in that situation is to contact our customer service, either by phone or live-chat. We do have a long queue but our agents are working  on it. 
https://t.co/O6Jy9vqnvM

//Kind regards, Dennis

@VictoriaXPalmer Hi!
When you have reported the bag missing, the tracing will immediately start. Once we have located your bag, you will be informed regarding delivery.

Best regards, Angelica

@signemelhaven Hi! 

If you have both flights in the same booking and one of them is cancelled then you can get a full refund for the whole trip. I recommend that you contact our customer service by phone or chat so we can help you: https://t.co/O6Jy9vqnvM

//Kind regards, Dennis

@hotstuffing2 Hi! 

Okay, i recommend that you contact our customer service in this case so we can help you with your booking.

//Kind regards, Dennis

@burna5 Hi! 

I'm sorry that your flight was affected by the strike. You can cancel your trip by using the link in your confirmation email or in My bookings at https://t.co/saQXo2wpQa

//Kind regards, Dennis

@theperpetualhi1 Hi @theperpetualhi1, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Mikael

@inna76se Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 you can then track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service at Lisbon at: +35 121 841 35 00
Kind regards, Rebecca

@jeremyhylton Hi, I am sorry to hear your bag is delayed. If you haven't reported your bag at the airport, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 You can track your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
or call baggage service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Rebecca

@MElvestuen Hi @MElvestuen,
One zero is missing at the end, the number is 0046 8 797 4100, please try that instead. We apologize for any inconvenience.
Kind regards, Mikael

@dmnicholson Hi @dmnicholson, we can't check the status in our system, that is handled by the arrival service at the airport where you landed. So please contact them for more information.
You can read more about delayed baggage here https://t.co/yaDBpcxdM2
Kind regards, Mikael.

@Alshehri_Fahad_ Hi! 

Okay, yes if you want to change the delivery address then you need to contact our baggage service by phone. You can find their number here: https://t.co/We1FdD7ZiM

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@vapersian Hi! 

We are usually able to put in an alternative if your flight is cancelled automatically but you may need to call us if you don't get any new information after your flight is cancelled. 
https://t.co/O6Jy9vqnvM

//Kind regards, Dennis

@scottsdalesanj Hi! 

I'm sorry that you are in that situation, but we sadly can't help you with that case from here. Our personnel are working on it as fast as possible, and they will contact you when your bag arrives. The best i can recommend for now is to wait.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@wavedavey Hi! 

Okay, i recommend that you contact our customer service either via phone or our live-chat so we can help you have a look at your trip.
https://t.co/O6Jy9v8M7c

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@mjoc Hi, you can view your booking under "my bookings" and apply for a refund.
Best regards,
Stina

@AcasceAntonio Hi, if your flight was cancelled you can contact us to look at rebooking options or a full refund. https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
Best regards,
Stina

@Kevster2121 Hi! 

Yes you can contact our customer service if your flight is cancelled. Please contact us via phone or our live-chat so we can help you have a look at the alternatives.
https://t.co/O6Jy9v8M7c

//Kind regards, 
Dennis

@Kevster2121 Hi, please contact us by chat or phone to look at rebooking options: https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
Best regards,
Stina

@FabricePerier Hi, if your flight is cancelled you can apply for a refund. Please view your booking under "my bookings" or contact us by chat or phone: https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
Best regards,
Stina

@PratyushMurark2 Hi! 

Yes you have to go through immigration in LHR in that case. 

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@astral_clouds Hi, we need to have a look at your booking to answer for your specific flight. Please contact us by chat or phone: https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
Best regards,
Stina

@naboushadi Hi, you are welcome to contact us by chat for help: https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
Best regards,
Stina

@maddie_a14 Hi, you can trace your bag here: https://t.co/2zwsPbzrxs , you can also contact bagage service for status on your luggage, numbers can be found here: https://t.co/ZV9bTNLSZs
Best regards,
Stina

@IWouldTweet4U Hi! 

Yes if you need to travel, for example if you are stranded on your destination, you may arrange alternative travel yourself and seek reimbursement from us afterwards. You can read more about it here: https://t.co/rFWuWiMY1m

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@onamonapiamaria Hi! 

Yes the best we can recommend in that situation is to try to keep it as low as possible, and then send us the receipts so Customer Care can have a look and see if we can compensate you.

//Kind regards, Dennis

@solitabonita100 Hi, if your flight is cancelled you are entitled to a full refund. If not cancelled the refund is based on your ticket rules.
Best regards,
Stina

@Oliver663206662 Hi, you are welcome to contact us by the chat if you are not getting through by phone. https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R
Best regards,
Stina

@deblasky Hi! 

I'm sorry that your are in that situation. We sadly can't see missing baggage reports from here, so the best we can recommend is to call the baggage service. We will of course contact you when your bags are found.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@jessie___m Hi, yes we do have an online chat, you can find it here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Best regards,
Stina

@Vnf88 Hi! 

I'm sorry if your flight was affected. We sadly don't know exactly when the strike will be over, but we are working on it as fast as possible. 

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@DavidWiederkehr Hi! 

I'm sorry if your flight was cancelled. We do send out a message about cancelled flights via email, but that email is sometimes blocked. The best i can recommend is to contact our customer service so we can help you have a closer look at your trip.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@onamonapiamaria Hi! 

Yes if his flight is cancelled then we will be able to help him get a full refund or rebook his flight. He can then send us a compensation request via our website after the trip to have a look at a possible compensation.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@scarson0707 Hi! 

We can help you rebook your trip to a Star Alliance flight if your current one is cancelled. So the best i can recommend is to wait a bit and see how it looks closer to departure.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@cme2828 Hi! 

I'm sorry that you receive that message. The best i can recommend in that case is to contact our customer service by phone or live chat. We do have a long queue right now due to the strike, but we will try to answer you as soon as possible.

//Kind regards,
Dennis

@Dorset_Viking Hi! 

Yes, you can contact our customer service by phone or live chat. You can find our contact information here: https://t.co/O6Jy9vqnvM

//Kind regards,
Dennis
